---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import MobileTease from '../../../components/MobileTease.astro';
const APP_URL = 'https://dev-app.audioask.ai';
---

<Layout
  title="Translate any podcast — 12 languages — Audioask"
  description="Translate any podcast into 12 languages and generate a dubbed audio episode with a voice of your choice."
  activePage="features"
  lang="en"
  alternatePath="/fonctionnalites/traduire"
>
<Fragment slot="head">
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
    "itemListElement": [
      { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "Home", "item": "https://www.audioask.ai/en" },
      { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "Features", "item": "https://www.audioask.ai/en/features" },
      { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 3, "name": "Translate", "item": "https://www.audioask.ai/en/features/translate" }
    ]
  })} />
</Fragment>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero dotbg">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="traduire-hero-grid" style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.05fr 1fr; gap: 64px; align-items: center;">
      <div>
        <div class="page-intro">Feature 04 · Translate <span style="margin-left: 8px; font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 10px; padding: 3px 9px; background: var(--ink); color: var(--cream); border-radius: 999px; letter-spacing: 0.06em;">COMING SOON</span></div>
        <h1 style="text-align: left;">
          Translate any podcast,<br>
          <span class="em-serif">in your language.</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="lede" style="margin-top: 24px;">
          Translate the transcript into 12 languages — and generate a new dubbed audio episode with a voice of your choice.
        </p>
        <div class="hero-ctas" style="margin-top: 32px;">
          <a class="btn btn-primary lg" href={`${APP_URL}/signup`}>Translate an episode <span class="arrow">→</span></a>
          <a class="btn lg" href="#">Listen to an example</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Translation card -->
      <div class="app-card traduire-hero-visual" style="max-width: 100%;">
        <div class="app-toolbar">
          <span class="dot"></span><span class="dot"></span><span class="dot"></span>
          <span class="url">audioask.ai · translation</span>
        </div>
        <div style="padding: 22px; background: var(--cream);">
          <div style="display: flex; gap: 12px; align-items: center;">
            <div style="padding: 8px 14px; background: var(--paper); border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 999px; display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center; font-size: 13px;">
              <span>🇺🇸</span><span>English</span>
            </div>
            <span style="color: var(--accent); font-size: 18px;">→</span>
            <div style="padding: 8px 14px; background: var(--accent); color: white; border-radius: 999px; display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center; font-size: 13px;">
              <span>🇫🇷</span><span>Français</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Side-by-side transcript -->
          <div style="margin-top: 16px; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 8px;">
            <div style="background: var(--paper); border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 12px; padding: 14px;">
              <div style="font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 9px; color: var(--ink-3); letter-spacing: 0.08em; margin-bottom: 8px;">ORIGINAL · 🇺🇸</div>
              <div style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.55; color: var(--ink-2);">
                <div style="margin-bottom: 6px;"><span style="font-family: var(--mono); color: var(--accent-ink); font-size: 10px; margin-right: 6px;">12:42</span>"We bet on CUDA when nobody believed in it."</div>
                <div><span style="font-family: var(--mono); color: var(--accent-ink); font-size: 10px; margin-right: 6px;">14:31</span>"Honestly, the board had doubts for three years."</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div style="background: var(--paper); border: 1px solid var(--accent); border-radius: 12px; padding: 14px;">
              <div style="font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 9px; color: var(--accent-ink); letter-spacing: 0.08em; margin-bottom: 8px;">TRANSLATED · 🇫🇷</div>
              <div style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.55; color: var(--ink);">
                <div style="margin-bottom: 6px;"><span style="font-family: var(--mono); color: var(--accent-ink); font-size: 10px; margin-right: 6px;">12:42</span>«&nbsp;On a parié sur CUDA quand personne n'y croyait.&nbsp;»</div>
                <div><span style="font-family: var(--mono); color: var(--accent-ink); font-size: 10px; margin-right: 6px;">14:31</span>«&nbsp;Honnêtement, le board avait des doutes pendant trois ans.&nbsp;»</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Audio dub -->
          <div style="margin-top: 14px; padding: 14px 16px; background: var(--paper); border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 12px;">
            <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 10px;">
              <span style="font-size: 12.5px; font-weight: 600;">✦ Dubbed audio · FR episode</span>
              <span class="chip accent-soft" style="font-size: 10.5px;">READY</span>
            </div>
            <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px;">
              <span style="width: 32px; height: 32px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--accent); color: white; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;">▶</span>
              <div style="flex: 1; height: 20px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 2px;">
                <span style="flex: 1; height: 14px; background: var(--accent); border-radius: 1px;"></span>
                <span style="flex: 1; height: 8px; background: var(--accent); border-radius: 1px;"></span>
                <span style="flex: 1; height: 18px; background: var(--accent); border-radius: 1px;"></span>
                <span style="flex: 1; height: 12px; background: var(--accent); border-radius: 1px;"></span>
                <span style="flex: 1; height: 20px; background: var(--accent); border-radius: 1px;"></span>
                <span style="flex: 1; height: 6px; background: var(--accent); border-radius: 1px;"></span>
                <span style="flex: 1; height: 16px; background: var(--accent); border-radius: 1px;"></span>
                <span style="flex: 1; height: 10px; background: var(--accent); border-radius: 1px;"></span>
                <span style="flex: 1; height: 14px; background: var(--accent); border-radius: 1px;"></span>
                <span style="flex: 1; height: 8px; background: var(--accent); border-radius: 1px;"></span>
                <span style="flex: 1; height: 18px; background: var(--accent); border-radius: 1px;"></span>
                <span style="flex: 1; height: 12px; background: var(--accent); border-radius: 1px;"></span>
                <span style="flex: 1; height: 20px; background: var(--cream-3); border-radius: 1px;"></span>
                <span style="flex: 1; height: 6px; background: var(--cream-3); border-radius: 1px;"></span>
                <span style="flex: 1; height: 14px; background: var(--cream-3); border-radius: 1px;"></span>
                <span style="flex: 1; height: 10px; background: var(--cream-3); border-radius: 1px;"></span>
                <span style="flex: 1; height: 16px; background: var(--cream-3); border-radius: 1px;"></span>
                <span style="flex: 1; height: 8px; background: var(--cream-3); border-radius: 1px;"></span>
              </div>
              <span style="font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 10px; color: var(--ink-3);">12:42 / 2:47:01</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- 12 LANGUAGES -->
<section class="section alt">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="center" style="max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto;">
      <div class="eyebrow center" style="justify-content: center; display: inline-flex;"><span class="dot">●</span> 12 languages</div>
      <h2 style="margin-top: 16px;">Your favourite podcasts,<br><span class="serif-it">in the language of your choice.</span></h2>
    </div>

    <div class="lang-grid">
      <div class="lang-chip on"><span class="flag">🇫🇷</span><span>Français</span></div>
      <div class="lang-chip"><span class="flag">🇬🇧</span><span>English</span></div>
      <div class="lang-chip"><span class="flag">🇩🇪</span><span>Deutsch</span></div>
      <div class="lang-chip"><span class="flag">🇮🇹</span><span>Italiano</span></div>
      <div class="lang-chip"><span class="flag">🇪🇸</span><span>Español</span></div>
      <div class="lang-chip"><span class="flag">🇵🇹</span><span>Português</span></div>
      <div class="lang-chip"><span class="flag">🇳🇱</span><span>Nederlands</span></div>
      <div class="lang-chip"><span class="flag">🇸🇪</span><span>Svenska</span></div>
      <div class="lang-chip"><span class="flag">🇯🇵</span><span>日本語</span></div>
      <div class="lang-chip"><span class="flag">🇰🇷</span><span>한국어</span></div>
      <div class="lang-chip"><span class="flag">🇨🇳</span><span>中文</span></div>
      <div class="lang-chip"><span class="flag">🇸🇦</span><span>العربية</span></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- FEATURES -->
<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div style="max-width: 720px;">
      <div class="eyebrow"><span class="dot">●</span> Under the hood</div>
      <h2 style="margin-top: 16px;">Three levels<br><span class="serif-it">of depth.</span></h2>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-alt" style="margin-top: 48px; border-top: 0;">
      <div>
        <div class="eyebrow"><span style="color: var(--accent);">01</span> · Collaborative model</div>
        <h3 style="margin-top: 12px;">One translation benefits everyone.</h3>
        <p>Like transcriptions, every translation enriches the shared library. If someone has already translated the episode into your language, access is instant.</p>
        <div style="margin-top: 24px; display: flex; align-items: baseline; gap: 12px;">
          <span style="font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 44px; line-height: 1; letter-spacing: -0.03em; color: var(--accent-ink);">12</span>
          <span style="font-size: 14px; color: var(--ink-3);">languages covered</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="demo" style="padding: 22px;">
        <div style="font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 10px; color: var(--ink-3); letter-spacing: 0.08em; margin-bottom: 12px;">AVAILABLE VERSIONS · #119 ACQUIRED</div>
        <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 6px;">
          <div style="background: var(--paper); border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 10px; padding: 10px 14px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; font-size: 13px;">
            <span style="font-size: 20px;">🇺🇸</span>
            <span style="flex: 1;">Original · English</span>
            <span style="font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 10px; color: var(--ink-3);">2h 47min</span>
          </div>
          <div style="background: var(--paper); border: 1px solid var(--accent); border-radius: 10px; padding: 10px 14px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; font-size: 13px;">
            <span style="font-size: 20px;">🇫🇷</span>
            <span style="flex: 1; font-weight: 600;">Français</span>
            <span class="chip accent-soft" style="height: 22px; font-size: 10.5px; padding: 0 8px;">ALREADY TRANSLATED · 0 credits</span>
          </div>
          <div style="background: var(--paper); border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 10px; padding: 10px 14px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; font-size: 13px;">
            <span style="font-size: 20px;">🇩🇪</span>
            <span style="flex: 1;">Deutsch</span>
            <span class="chip accent-soft" style="height: 22px; font-size: 10.5px; padding: 0 8px;">ALREADY TRANSLATED</span>
          </div>
          <div style="background: var(--paper); border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 10px; padding: 10px 14px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; font-size: 13px; color: var(--ink-3);">
            <span style="font-size: 20px;">🇮🇹</span>
            <span style="flex: 1;">Italiano</span>
            <span class="chip" style="height: 22px; font-size: 10.5px; padding: 0 8px; background: var(--cream-2); border-color: var(--line);">→ Translate</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-alt reverse">
      <div>
        <div class="eyebrow"><span style="color: var(--accent);">02</span> · Dubbed audio</div>
        <h3 style="margin-top: 12px;">A new audio episode. <span class="serif-it">Dubbed.</span></h3>
        <p>Not just a text translation: generate a true dubbed audio episode, preserving the pace and voices of each speaker.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="demo" style="padding: 22px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 12px;">
        <div style="font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 10px; color: var(--ink-3); letter-spacing: 0.08em;">DUBBED EPISODE · #119 FR</div>
        <div style="background: var(--paper); border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 14px; padding: 16px;">
          <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px;">
            <div style="width: 48px; height: 48px; border-radius: 10px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #5B7FD9, #2E4FB5); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; color: white; font-weight: 700; font-size: 12px;">#119</div>
            <div style="flex: 1;">
              <div style="font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600;">Nvidia · the decade</div>
              <div style="font-size: 11.5px; color: var(--ink-3);">Acquired · 🇫🇷 dubbed audio</div>
            </div>
            <span style="width: 36px; height: 36px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--accent); color: white; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;">▶</span>
          </div>
          <div style="margin-top: 12px; height: 4px; background: var(--cream-2); border-radius: 2px; position: relative;">
            <div style="position: absolute; left: 0; top: 0; bottom: 0; width: 22%; background: var(--accent); border-radius: 2px;"></div>
            <div style="position: absolute; top: 50%; left: 22%; transform: translateY(-50%); width: 10px; height: 10px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--accent);"></div>
          </div>
          <div style="margin-top: 8px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 10px; color: var(--ink-3);">
            <span>0:36:42</span><span>2:47:01</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-alt">
      <div>
        <div class="eyebrow"><span style="color: var(--accent);">03</span> · Voice selection</div>
        <h3 style="margin-top: 12px;">Choose the voice for each speaker.</h3>
        <p>For each identified speaker, select a voice from our library — or clone your own voice (Pro plan).</p>
      </div>
      <div class="demo" style="padding: 22px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px;">
        <div style="font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 10px; color: var(--ink-3); letter-spacing: 0.08em;">SPEAKERS · 3 DETECTED</div>
        <div class="voice-card">
          <div class="voice-avatar">BG</div>
          <div style="flex: 1; min-width: 0;">
            <div style="font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600;">Ben Gilbert</div>
            <div style="font-size: 11px; color: var(--ink-3);">Audioask voice · "Marc · deep · FR"</div>
          </div>
          <div class="voice-wave">
            <span style="height: 30%"></span><span style="height: 60%"></span><span style="height: 40%"></span><span style="height: 80%"></span><span style="height: 30%"></span><span style="height: 70%"></span><span style="height: 50%"></span><span style="height: 90%"></span><span style="height: 30%"></span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="voice-card">
          <div class="voice-avatar" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #5B7FD9, #2E4FB5);">DR</div>
          <div style="flex: 1; min-width: 0;">
            <div style="font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600;">David Rosenthal</div>
            <div style="font-size: 11px; color: var(--ink-3);">Audioask voice · "Antoine · medium · FR"</div>
          </div>
          <div class="voice-wave">
            <span style="height: 50%; background: #5B7FD9;"></span><span style="height: 30%; background: #5B7FD9;"></span><span style="height: 70%; background: #5B7FD9;"></span><span style="height: 40%; background: #5B7FD9;"></span><span style="height: 80%; background: #5B7FD9;"></span><span style="height: 50%; background: #5B7FD9;"></span><span style="height: 30%; background: #5B7FD9;"></span><span style="height: 60%; background: #5B7FD9;"></span><span style="height: 40%; background: #5B7FD9;"></span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="voice-card">
          <div class="voice-avatar" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6B6B6B, #3D3D3D);">JH</div>
          <div style="flex: 1; min-width: 0;">
            <div style="font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600;">Jensen Huang <span class="chip" style="height: 18px; padding: 0 6px; font-size: 9px; font-family: var(--mono); background: var(--ink); color: var(--cream); border: 0; margin-left: 4px;">PRO · CLONE</span></div>
            <div style="font-size: 11px; color: var(--ink-3);">Cloned voice · Jensen Huang FR</div>
          </div>
          <div class="voice-wave">
            <span style="height: 40%; background: var(--ink);"></span><span style="height: 70%; background: var(--ink);"></span><span style="height: 50%; background: var(--ink);"></span><span style="height: 90%; background: var(--ink);"></span><span style="height: 30%; background: var(--ink);"></span><span style="height: 60%; background: var(--ink);"></span><span style="height: 80%; background: var(--ink);"></span><span style="height: 40%; background: var(--ink);"></span><span style="height: 70%; background: var(--ink);"></span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Bonus: automation -->
    <div class="feature-alt reverse" style="background: var(--cream-2); border-radius: 24px; padding: 48px; margin-top: 32px; border: 1px solid var(--line);">
      <div>
        <div style="display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;">
          <span style="background: var(--accent); color: white; padding: 4px 10px; border-radius: 999px; font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 0.08em;">BONUS · AUTO</span>
          <span class="eyebrow"><span style="color: var(--accent);">04</span> · Automation</span>
        </div>
        <h3 style="margin-top: 16px;">Automatically translate every new episode.</h3>
        <p>Combine with automations: every new episode of a followed channel is transcribed + translated + dubbed, delivered in the language of your choice.</p>
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/en/features/automate" style="margin-top: 20px;">See automations <span class="arrow">→</span></a>
      </div>
      <div class="demo" style="padding: 22px;">
        <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px;">
          <div style="display: flex; gap: 10px; align-items: center; font-size: 13px; padding: 10px 14px; background: var(--paper); border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 10px;">
            <span style="color: var(--accent);">
              <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" stroke="none"><path d="M13 2L4 14h7l-1 8 9-12h-7l1-8z"/></svg>
            </span>
            <span style="flex: 1;"><b>Acquired</b> · new episode published</span>
            <span style="font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 10px; color: var(--ink-3);">12:14</span>
          </div>
          <div style="display: flex; gap: 10px; align-items: center; font-size: 13px; padding: 10px 14px; background: var(--paper); border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 10px;">
            <span style="color: var(--accent);">○</span>
            <span style="flex: 1;">Transcription EN</span>
            <span style="font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 10px; color: var(--accent);">2:48</span>
          </div>
          <div style="display: flex; gap: 10px; align-items: center; font-size: 13px; padding: 10px 14px; background: var(--paper); border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 10px;">
            <span style="color: var(--accent);">○</span>
            <span style="flex: 1;">Translation FR</span>
            <span style="font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 10px; color: var(--accent);">0:42</span>
          </div>
          <div style="display: flex; gap: 10px; align-items: center; font-size: 13px; padding: 10px 14px; background: var(--paper); border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 10px;">
            <span style="color: var(--accent);">○</span>
            <span style="flex: 1;">Dubbed audio FR</span>
            <span style="font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 10px; color: var(--accent);">5:18</span>
          </div>
          <div style="display: flex; gap: 10px; align-items: center; font-size: 13px; padding: 10px 14px; background: var(--accent-tint); border: 1px solid var(--accent); border-radius: 10px;">
            <span style="color: var(--accent);">●</span>
            <span style="flex: 1; color: var(--accent-ink); font-weight: 600;">✓ Delivered to library · 12:22</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<MobileTease lang="en" />

<!-- FAQ -->
<section class="section alt">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="center" style="max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto;">
      <div class="eyebrow center" style="justify-content: center; display: inline-flex;"><span class="dot">●</span> FAQ</div>
      <h2 style="margin-top: 16px;">Questions about <span class="serif-it">translation.</span></h2>
    </div>
    <div class="faq">
      <div class="faq-item">
        <span>How good is the dubbed audio quality?</span><span class="plus">+</span>
        <div class="faq-answer">Dubbed audio is generated by the latest speech synthesis models. The result is natural and preserves the original podcast's cadence. Quality varies depending on the selected voice.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <span>How long does dubbed audio generation take?</span><span class="plus">+</span>
        <div class="faq-answer">Audio generation typically takes a few minutes for a one-hour episode. The delay depends on our server load and the episode's duration.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <span>Can I clone my own voice?</span><span class="plus">+</span>
        <div class="faq-answer">Yes, voice cloning is available on the Pro plan. You simply provide a few minutes of audio recording of your voice to create a clone usable for dubbing.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <span>Are original podcasters notified?</span><span class="plus">+</span>
        <div class="faq-answer">No, translations remain in your personal Audioask space. They are not redistributed or published without your consent.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <span>Which languages support dubbed audio?</span><span class="plus">+</span>
        <div class="faq-answer">Dubbed audio is available for all 12 languages supported by Audioask: French, English, German, Italian, Spanish, Portuguese, Dutch, Swedish, Japanese, Korean, Chinese and Arabic.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CTA -->
<section class="section dark cta-final">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Translate your first episode<br><span class="em-serif">into 12 languages.</span></h2>
    <p class="lede" style="margin: 0 auto 36px; max-width: 50ch; color: var(--night-text-2);">
      Translation included in the Premium plan. Dubbed audio with Pro.
    </p>
    <a class="btn btn-primary lg" href={`${APP_URL}/signup`} style="height: 56px; font-size: 16px; padding: 0 28px;">Try now <span class="arrow">→</span></a>
  </div>
